Oral Squamous Cell Carcinoma.

Tahmasebi E(1), Kaboudanian Ardestani A(2), Madihi N(3), Abbasiparashkouh Z(4), 
Abbasi Maleki S(5), Yazdanian M(6), Khafaei M(7), Movafagh A(8), Tavallaie M(9).

